        public void onDoneButtonPressed(android.view.View v)
        A button-specific method, this gets called when you click the "Done" button. This writes the current objects into an XML file located in the Configuration File Directory. The user is prompted for the name of the file.
        Parameters:
        v - the View from which this was called
